Subject: [PATCH] net: use skb_list_del_init() to remove from RX sublists
References: bnc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 4.19.10
Git-commit: 22f6bbb7bcfcef0b373b0502a7ff390275c575dd

[ Upstream commit 22f6bbb7bcfcef0b373b0502a7ff390275c575dd ]

